# Pres23RodoHonsMultPCA

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of Pres23RodoHonsMultPCA is to create slides for the PCA section of the stats honours multivariate module 2023.

## Installation

You can install the development version of Pres23RodoHonsMultPCA like so:

``` r
if (!requireNamespace("devtools")) install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("MiguelRodo/Pres23RodoHonsMultPCA")
```
